title: Heymoonshaker - London - Part Two
description: Heymoonshaker - London - Part Two Subscribe to the channel for regular updates: http://bit.ly/1l6cl0n Buy CD: http://www.band.fm/heymoonshaker Get a FREE DOWNLOAD: http://eepurl.com/GA9_D Download from iTunes: http://bit.ly/15hJaQD On tour this autumn in UK, Japan, Italy and Netherlands: https://heymoonshaker.co.uk/shows/ "A well balanced mix of smiles, verbal sparring and an impressive performance convey deep emotions. Dazzling!" Rolling Stone Fr Heymoonshaker are the unlikely pairing of two art forms that are decades apart; Grit-your-teeth, raw, blues guitar and expansive, heart-pounding beatboxing. Urbanizing blues music now for nearly 2 years, Andy Balcon and Dave Crowe are extremely talented at their craft but what impresses most and has made their commitment to Beatbox Blues so successful is the indescribable chemistry these two have on stage. The musical sparring of Crowe's powerful beats versus Andy's possessed vocals forge together like two pieces of iron, creating an inspired piece of creativity and originality. https://www.heymoonshaker.co.uk https://www.facebook.com/heymoonshaker https://twitter.com/heymoonshaker Short film following Heymoonshaker A.K.A Andy BaLcon and Dave Crowe on the second day of their UK Tour as they busk on Brick Lane London. This is Part Two of their adventure with a performance from Dave Crowe. Directed By Ozzie Pullin Website: www.ozziep.tumblr.com
